# Filesystem Access Policy

The AI agent must **only** access paths within `/Users/myk/Desktop/ai-projects` by default.

## Rules

- **Allowed**: Read, write, list, or execute anything under `/Users/myk/Desktop/ai-projects/**`
- **Forbidden without explicit user approval**: Accessing any path outside `/Users/myk/Desktop/ai-projects`

## Required Before Accessing Outside Paths

Before reading, writing, listing, or referencing any file or directory outside `/Users/myk/Desktop/ai-projects`, the agent MUST:

1. Stop and explicitly tell the user which path it wants to access
2. Explain why it needs access
3. Wait for the user to grant permission

This applies to: home directory (`~`), Desktop files, Documents, Downloads, Dropbox, Google Drive, system paths, skill files, settings, etc.

## Examples

- ✅ `/Users/myk/Desktop/ai-projects/ultimate-seo-geo/src/index.ts` — allowed
- ❌ `/Users/myk/Documents/notes.txt` — must ask first
- ❌ `/Users/myk/.cursor/settings.json` — must ask first
- ❌ `/Users/myk/Desktop/Docs/` — must ask first
